Params: {2: 'Bianca', 3: 'You seemed a little upset during the evening when you had to leave.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I also think our date shouldn't end like that, which is why I want to give it a proper conclusion.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Let's go, Commandant. I'll walk you back.", 4: '1'}
{2: "I wouldn't want to trouble you!", 3: '18', 4: "That's very kind of you.", 5: '19'}
{3: 'Silence fills the air at once. All you can hear is the sound of your overlapping footsteps.'}
{2: 'Did you have a good time today—', 3: '25'}
{2: 'You first.', 3: '104', 4: 'What were you trying to say?', 5: '104'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Going to gatherings with you, cooking for you, and watching a movie with you has made me very happy.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Perhaps my usual sternness has not made me very popular.', 4: '1'}
{2: "That's not true. That's what made you Bianca.", 3: '33', 4: "No way, Bianca. You're first on the Date-a-Construct chart!", 5: '34'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'But it troubles me sometimes as well.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Anyway, it troubles me sometimes as well.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Why would I have conflicting thoughts when I claim to abide by my faith...?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Your faith creates the very foundation of who you are.', 3: '41'}
{2: 'And those conflicts... smooth out the edges.', 3: '43'}
{2: 'Of course. When have I ever lied to you?', 3: '47'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "You're right. I've chosen this path, and I will see it through.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'I will sacrifice everything for what I believe to be "right" until the day the Punishing Virus vanishes from this Earth.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'I admire your kindness.', 3: '52', 4: 'I admire your determination.', 5: '50'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Commandant... why do you think I'm determined?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Commandant... why do you think I'm kind?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Why do you act so prudent on your missions, Bianca?', 3: '56', 4: 'Why did you join the Purifying Force, Bianca?', 5: '57'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "It's illogical to carry out purification when I have not confirmed the risks the targets pose with my own investigations.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Those infected Constructs... are in such unimaginable pain that someone has to free them from their torments.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'I had a lovely time today.', 3: '101', 4: "I'm glad I could go on a date with you.", 5: '61'}
{2: "You know? You don't have to envy me at all.", 3: '66'}
{2: 'Whoa. That was fast.', 3: '71', 4: "Can't believe a lady walked me home!", 5: '71'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Then, I think this concludes our date. Properly.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I'll see you again, Gray Raven Commandant.", 4: '1'}
